nit, constexpr

I was thinking that this would be the last addition to the privilege registry and any override information should go into a new privilege_override_registry. This is because the map still pertains to the base privilege set given by the registry. I am happy to move it if you can come up with a better filename than "privilege_registry_map.hpp". Also would it just be that singular map in the file or should the enums be moved too
